old sailing ship.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3870, \"end\": 3883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0110346153152977e-22, \"text\": \"Olympic flame\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\"}, {\"begin\": 3902, \"end\": 3908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999871653108691, \"rank\": 1.283484534896392e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 3941, \"end\": 3946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bel\\u00e9m\", \"score\": 0.9903282791598326, \"rank\": 0.00799898425596817, \"text\": \"Belem\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bel\\u00e9m\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bel\\u00e9m\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will sail across the Mediterranean Sea for 12 days, in a 2000 kilometre journey that will see it dock for the port city of Marseille in France.\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 4124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4104, \"end\": 4113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999999999422471, \"rank\": 4.5715677416783266e-11, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 4117, \"end\": 4123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999949035440274, \"rank\": 1.939910372777731e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is due to arrive on 8 May.\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The flame will then travel across France, including its overseas